description: This file contains unit tests for the UserSettings component, using Google Test and Google Mock frameworks. It tests various getter and setter methods of user settings, ensuring correct handling of success and failure scenarios, and validating input parameters.

classes.name: UserSettingsTest
classes.description: A test fixture class for testing the UserSettings component functionalities, using Google Test framework. Sets up mocks and handles test initialization and cleanup.
